# Lines starting with # are comments
# https://github.com/ytdl-org/youtube-dl
#
# All options can be overriden on the command line for a specific download

# Format options:
# Download bestvideo and bestaudio file separately and merge them using ffmpeg
# or download the best quality single file.
# https://github.com/ytdl-org/youtube-dl#format-selection
--format 'bestvideo+bestaudio/best'

# Output format:
# Also acts as a way to specify a default download location
# https://github.com/ytdl-org/youtube-dl#output-template
--output '~/Downloads/youtube/%(title)s.%(ext)s'

# Restrict filenames to only ASCII characters, and avoid "&" and spaces in filenames
--restrict-filenames

# vim: ft=conf
